  <section>
    <h2>4. Fitting Parameters of V-VTEAM Model</h2>
    <p class="caption">Testing value와 fitting value 비교</p>
    <div class="table-box">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Testing Value</th><th>Fitting Value</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
